Date: Mon, 30 Mar 2026 15:13:33 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 36/40] build: split keep RTLIL and JSON extraction into
 separate actions
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- synth_keep.tcl now only writes 1_1_yosys_keep.rtlil (no JSON)
- rtlil_kept_modules.py extracts kept_modules.json from the RTLIL
- New Makefile target do-yosys-kept-json for the fast Python step
- Blackbox before hierarchy check in synth.tcl (catch unknown modules)
- Unit test for RTLIL parsing

This allows fast iteration on the JSON format without re-running Yosys.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>
Signed-off-by: Øyvind Harboe <oyvind.harboe@zylin.com>
